flowchart TD
  S[SCHEDULE] --> V{Votes allowed?}
  V -- Yes --> SV[Schedule votes]
  V -- No --> CB{Bundle allowed and ready?}
  SV --> CB
  CB -- Yes, no votes scheduled --> SB[Try schedule bundle]
  SB -- Success --> OUT
  SB -- Conflict/No --> NT
  CB -- No --> NT[Schedule normal txns]
  NT --> OUT[Publish microblock + trailer]



